The stroke size, in relative pixels, of the item border. The border is created to the inside of the item, and its color can be set by using the [bordercolor](Bordercolor_%28GUI_item_property%29 "Bordercolor (GUI item property)") property.

The value of this property cannot be changed at runtime.

Syntax
------

    bordersize size

Default value
-------------

    0

Example(s)
----------

    bordersize 1


